Yuan REIT May Be Launched, Hong Kong Exchanges Says

-- B y   F i o n   L i
-- 
2011-02-15T09:08:04Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-15/yuan-reit-may-be-launched-hong-kong-exchanges-says-update1-.html
The first yuan-denominated equity
product in Hong Kong is likely to be a real estate investment
trust and simulations for trading will be held on March 19-20,
said Romnesh Lamba, head of market development at  Hong Kong 
Exchanges and Clearing Ltd.  Cheung Kong (Holdings) Ltd. may offer a 3.6 percent yield
on its planned yuan REIT, the Oriental Daily reported on Feb. 14.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Fion Li in Hong Kong at 
